data.description: Assumable Loan Available with a 3% Interest Rate! 1 Owner Home, Like New, Move-In Ready 3 Bedroom 2.5 Bath Contemporary Style Home Less Than 10 Minutes from Downtown San Antonio & Pearl Brewery.  Interior Features Open Floor and High Ceilings with Ceramic Tile Throughout. Spacious Island Kitchen Offers Granite Counters, Custom Soft Close Cabinets, Stainless Steel Appliances and Plenty of Cabinet and Counter Space. Large Master Bedroom Features Tons of Natural Light with Full Bath Offering Double Vanity, Walk-In Closet and Oversized Mud Set Shower. Spacious Secondary Bedrooms Great for Guest or Kids. Exterior Features Gated Front Entry, 2 Car Carport, Oversized Covered Patio in Backyard and Fully Fenced Yard with added Storage Shed for Extra Storage. Located Minutes to Highways I-35 and I-10 with Shopping and Restaurants only Minutes Away. No Creative Financing will be Considered.
